node.text: @bawkii I will till I can’t no more! 😊🙏🏻
Amazing! Keep chasing, capturing, and sharing! 🧡🙌

@lindseymbrown1986 nothing comes natural with photography lol I wish though. I do think I see things that other people may miss. It took a lot of trial and error with my photography to get it to where it is today 😊. I put a lot of thought and time into most of my shots. It’s all about finding the right composition to a photo. That’s what can make it really stand out. It has to tell a story or be visually appealing.
@photographyinfocus yeah I was just wondering you do great work just didnt know about if you took courses or classes either way I love your work always capturing some of the best photos I've seen
@lindseymbrown1986 all self taught. I watched a lot of YouTube videos. I also have a lot of photography friends. I’ve picked up things here and there along the way 🙂

Absolutely stunning and magnificent. This photo is so  BEAUTIFUL you do such a wonderful job at capturing your photos you were born to do photography for SURE @photographyinfocus  quick question did it come natural something you've always loved and done or did you take any classes?  just curious I keep seeing things about classes for and it's always been something I loved doing I always took photos as a child and still do just with small cameras but thats all I had I just didnt know if you took any courses
So lovely as always! 🌞🔥 this one is especially captivating.
